parameters: The air is quiet, with no sound, and a cool breeze blows.

In this place where only the sound of the waves can be
heard, only the sounds created by the two of them can
be clearly heard.
A man and a woman holding hands in the water.
The atmosphere is like a shoujo manga.

The only thing that bothers me is that the roles of the
man and woman are reversed... but I'll try not to worry
about it.

I thought the atmosphere had become quite nice, so I
began to ask in a serious tone.
Sensei, sensei. There's something I want to ask you.
Yes, Hikaru-kun. What is it that you want to ask?
I'm curious why Akane-chan's breasts are so big.
H-Hikaru...! What are you thinking right now...?!
Kyaa!? Don't stick your face in...!
Geez... Can't you be a little more serious...

I specifically came out here because Hikaru asked me to
teach him how to swim...

I cool my head a little with the water Akane poured on
me.
Even so, I can't help but feel regretful.
Specifically, the lower half of my body...

When I'm this close to Akane, any guy would end up like
this.
Kyaaah! I told you not to get your face close...!
Huh? Let's do it here, Akane.
No one should be coming, so it should be fine.
Today, the moon is bright for some reason...
Geez! What if someone sees us?!
I won't be able to get married for real.
